Package: fatEstimator
Title: Forecasted Average Treatment Effect Estimation via Polynomial Regression
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Laura", "Zell", email = "laura.zell@stud.unilu.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Forecasted Average Treatment (FAT) estimator for policy 
    evaluation using polynomial regression on pre-treatment outcomes. The package 
    allows flexible estimation across user-defined degrees and forecast horizons, 
    with optional bootstrapped standard errors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
